  <p>To quickly get to the full <app>Evolution</app> calendar, click on the
  clock and click <gui>Open Calendar</gui>.</p>

  <note>
    <p>This will work only if you have an existing <app>Evolution</app>
    account. Otherwise, a window will appear with the necessary steps for
    adding your first account.</p>
  </note>

